<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yī zhǔ yī xìn yī xǐ yī shén 迦南1028</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yī zhǔ yī xìn yī xǐ yī shén, tóng méng tiān shàng qí yì jiù ēn. yé sū jī dū shì fáng jiǎo shí, wǒ men kào tā tóng bèi jiàn wěn.
 wú lùn jīn shì duō shǎo fēng yǔ, xìn kào yé sū yǒng gǎn yì lì. jiào huì yī dìng yào fā zhēn guāng, zhǔ shì wéi yī dé jiù gēn jī.
 jǐng xǐng xìng qǐ shén de ér nǚ, wú lùn jīn shì duō shǎo fēng yǔ. làng dǎ de shí xuě yā de sōng, xìn kào yé sū yǒng gǎn yì lì.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1028</hymn_number>
</song>